'''[[ballast]] [[tank]]'''
#One of several [[external]] or [[internal]] tanks fitted in [[submarine]]s; when filled with [[seawater]] they allow the [[boat]] to [[submerge]]; when emptied using [[compressed air]] [[buoyancy]] is restored and the vessel rises towards the [[surface]]. [[Auxiliary]] ballast tanks within the [[pressure hull]] allow the submarine to be [[trimmed]].
